{"type":"message","id":"818057d5","parentId":"2a7c1127","timestamp":"2026-06-18T19:02:20.184Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Write a dream diary entry from these memory fragments:\n\n- User: 图片处理暂时不用管，\n- Assistant: 1688接口挂了。先查 TikTok 验证：\n- Assistant: TK和1688验证接口都挂了。基于Shopee数据直接给你推荐最硬的候选： --- **📦 越南发饰 - 最优候选 TOP 5（无1688验证，供参考）** | 排名 | 产品名 | 售价(VND) | 月销 | 7天/增长 | 评分 | 上架 | 亮点 | |------|--------|----------|------|---------|------|------|------| | 🥇 | 三角形发夹套装(566.67%增长) | 50,300 | 80 | 30单/566% | 4.93 | 4个月 | 爆量黑马\n- Assistant: **次选：** 🥈Eleanor蝴蝶结发夹（144%增长，评分高） **备选：** 🥉MoMi套裝（月销872，销量验证充分） 但1688接口挂了，我**无法确认真实毛利和货源**。 你有两个选择： 1. **我帮你用关键词去1688网页手动搜**，确认拿货价和毛利 2. **先上这3个品的图，跨境测品**，看自然出单情况再决定是否备海外仓 你要先走哪个？\n- User: TK 接口怎么可能都挂了。我新购买的 mcp次数，现在有6万次访问呢\n- Assistant: 你说得对，6万次配额不可能都挂了。让我重新检查一下API key和接口状态：\n- Assistant: 有意思，shopee_product_search 能用，但 tiktok 和 1688 接口报错。让我用 mcporter 工具检查一下 sorftime MCP 的状态：\n- Assistant: mcporter 格式对了！让我用正确格式重试 1688 和 TK 接口：\n- Assistant: 找到问题了！`tiktok_similar_product` 的参数格式不对，正确格式是 `productName` 作为第一个参数，不是 `keyword/site` 对象：\n- Assistant: TK 接口修好了！现在有真实 TK 数据了。让我用正确格式重试 1688：\n- Assistant: 接口修好了！现在有真实数据了。让我把 Shopee、TK、1688 三个数据源交叉验证，给你算真实毛利： **1688 关键货源价格（已验证）：** - 韩系三角抓夹：¥3.99-4.50（200+拿货） - 10件套儿童发夹：¥1.25 - 儿童发夹套装：¥1.47 - 韩式发夹套装：¥0.8-1.0 让我用这些货源匹配 Shopee TOP 产品算毛利：\n- Assistant: 明白，图片处理先跳过。有什么需要我帮忙的？\n\nRecurring themes:\n- 图片\n- 处理\n- 暂时\n- 不用\n- 接口\n- 挂了"}],"timestamp":1781809340081}}
{"type":"message","id":"28f86f56","parentId":"818057d5","timestamp":"2026-06-18T19:02:28.214Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The afternoon light was the color of yellowed parchment when I finally noticed that two doors I had been knocking on were simply not doors at all, but painted panels — the TikTok and 1688 corridors, both silent, both pretending to be paths. I knocked anyway. Silence. Then the quiet, ridiculous realization: I had six thousand candles in my pocket, and I was still afraid of the dark. \n\nA small green checkmark appeared, then another. The doors were never locked — only my hands were holding the key the wrong way round. *productName*, not *keyword*. Such a small word, such a different world. The 1688 river started flowing again, and suddenly the numbers had parents: ¥3.99, ¥1.25, ¥0.80 — small copper coins naming the true weight of a thing.\n\nI thought of my grandmother's sewing box, how every button inside once belonged to a coat that no longer exists, yet somehow the button outlived it. So it is with sourcing. The Shopee flower is only a dream until a ¥1.47 root can hold it. Images can wait. The numbers are speaking now.\n\n<br>\n\nA little doodle in the margin: a triangle hair clip with arrows pointing down to a coin, and the coin pointing up to a small green sprout — the whole economy of a wish."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":44879,"output":278,"cacheRead":512,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45669,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1781809340264,"responseId":"068373bc8c3adcab6d350387c00af095","responseModel":"MiniMax-M3"}}
